	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissime idemque ornatissime vir, domine amice noster plurimum charissime ac observande.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Propensam benevolentiam nostram ac omne genus officii excellentissimae dominationi vestrae deferimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum hic illustri loco natus adolescens spectabilis et magnificus dominus <persName type="auto_name">Ioannes Kysska</persName>, palatinides <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2571" cert="high">Witebczensis</placeName>, liber baro in <placeName type="citizen_name">Cziechanowyecz</placeName>, in <placeName type="citizen_name">Tivye</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name">Losko</placeName> dominus, in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName> capessendae virtutis et rectae institutionis causa proficisceretur, nostrum consilium sequutus statuit inprimis vestram rempublicam et scholam Tigurinam videre ac in illa conversari.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Noluimus itaque intermittere, quae est nostra in praestantiam tuam voluntatis et officii affectio quaque benevolentia per mutuas literas constituta, quin adolescentem praestantiae tuae commendaremus, ut eum vel nostra causa benevolentia et favoribus suis prosequatur, et quicquid porro in eum humanitatis hospitalitatisque contulerit, id eo loco habituri sumus ac ita accepturi, ac si in nos met ipsos vel filiolum nostrum non ita pridem etiam ad vos ablegatum hoc officii esset collocatum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De reliquo cupimus praestantiae tuae firmam valetudinem et plurimam omnium bonarum foelicitatum accessionem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilnae</placeName> die 26. augusti anno domini 1563.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Excellentissimae dominationis vestrae bonus amicus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8117" cert="high">Nicolaus Radziwyl</persName>, dei gratia in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2573" cert="high">Olyka</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2572" cert="high">Nieswyess</placeName> dux, dominus in <placeName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="l250">Klyeczko</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2584" cert="high">Grodek</placeName>, palatinus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilnensis</placeName>, magni ducatus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l841" cert="high">Lithuaniae</placeName> supremus marssalcus et archicancellarius <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l626" cert="high">Brzestensis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2570" cert="high">Kawnensis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2585" cert="high">Borissoviensis</placeName> et in magna <placeName type="citizen_name">Schawlye</placeName> capitaneus generalis etc. manu propria subscripsit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo eidemque doctissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bulingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tigurinae pastori vigilantissimo ac ecclesiarum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helveticarum</placeName> superintendenti dignissimo, amico nostro charissimo ac observandissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
